benchmark_config.jira_title: Implement/Test API: PUT /1.0/kb/invoicePayments/{paymentId}/customFields - Modify custom fields to payment

Successful modification with all optional headers (TC02)
Successful modification when no custom fields exist initially (TC03)
Successful modification with empty custom fields array (TC04)

gaps: No tests explicitly cover pagination handling for large datasets.
Authorization scenarios beyond missing header are not tested.
No tests for rate limiting or throttling behavior.
Caching headers and caching behavior are not tested.
No explicit tests for concurrency issues beyond race conditions implied.
No tests for partial updates or concurrency conflicts.
No tests for soft delete or data recovery scenarios.
recommendations: Add tests for pagination handling with large datasets.
Include authorization tests for different user roles and token validity.
Implement rate limiting and throttling tests.
Test caching headers like ETag and Cache-Control for GET responses.
Add concurrency and race condition tests for simultaneous updates.
Include tests for partial updates and conflict resolution.
Test soft delete or data recovery mechanisms if applicable.
